article_id:1170,category_name:News,title_name:Platinum Showcase 1 Is Now Live! Featured 5★ Adventurer Guaranteed!,image_path:,message:<div>Platinum Showcase 1 went live <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1585288800"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div>Platinum Showcase 1 is a limited summon showcase that works similarly to a tenfold summon in that one summon will get you 10 results. The difference between a regular tenfold summon and this Platinum Showcase is that one of the featured 5★ adventurers&mdash;Gala Luca, Gala Cleo, Gala Ranzal, or Gala Sarisse&mdash;is guaranteed to appear.</div><div><br></div><div>During the period, players are limited to doing this Platinum Showcase summon only once, and these summons can only be performed with diamantium (purchase required).</div><div><br></div><div><span style="color: rgb(226, 80, 65);">・The roster for this summon showcase does not include the new Gala Alex adventurer from the Gala Dragalia summon showcase, which is live at the same time.</span></div><div><span style="color: rgb(226, 80, 65);">・The roster for this summon showcase includes the featured 5★ adventurers eligible for guaranteed summons in Platinum Showcase 2, which is live at the same time, but they are not eligible for guaranteed summons in this showcase.</span></div><div><br></div><div>Availability period for Platinum Showcase 1:</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1585288800"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1586757540"></span></div><div><br></div><div>Get a closer look at the 5★ adventurers eligible to appear as the guaranteed 5★ summon for Platinum Showcase 1.</div><div><br></div><div>5★ adventurers eligible for guaranteed appearance as the 10th summon:</div><div><br></div><div>
